plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.name: BT7_Rev_ProdTypeKey
plmxml_bus:SavedQueryDef.Description: ProdTypeKey Revision search with specific attributes

plmxml_bus:QueryClause.stringValue: SELECT qid FROM BT7_ProdTypeKeyRevision WHERE "object_type" = "${ObjectType = BT7_ProdTypeKeyRevision}" AND "items_tag.item_id" = "${ItemID = }" AND "object_name" = "${ItemName_EN = }" AND "bt7_ItemRevName_2" = "${ItemName_DE = }" AND "bt7_Subtitle_1" = "${Subtitle_EN = }" AND "bt7_Subtitle_2" = "${Subtitle_DE = }" AND "BT7_ProdTypeKey:items_tag.bt7_EqPartNo" = "${Alternate Number = }" AND "bt7_documentClass" = "${bt7_documentClass = }" AND "bt7_documentSubClass" = "${bt7_documentSubClass = }" AND "bt7_documentSNType" = "${bt7_documentSNType = }" AND "item_revision_id" = "${Revision = }" AND "bt7_FirstUse" = "${FirstUse = }" AND "bt7_RevLastStatus" = "${Releasestatus = }" AND "date_released" <= "${Releasedbefore = }" AND "bt7_docmnumber" = "${ECONumber = }" AND "owning_user.user_id" = "${Creator = }" AND "owning_group.name" = "${OwningGroup = }" AND "creation_date" >= "${Createdafter = }" AND "creation_date" <= "${Createdbefore = }" AND "last_mod_user.user_id" = "${LastMod.User = }" AND "last_mod_date" >= "${Changedafter = }" AND "last_mod_date" <= "${Changedbefore = }"
